  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large Dutch oven, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the lamb shoulder and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the smoked paprika, cumin, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the Korean pear, kombu cold extract, and chicken broth, and bring to a boil.",
    "Cover the Dutch oven and transfer to the preheated oven.",
    "Braise the lamb for 2.5 hours, or until tender.",
    "Remove the Dutch oven from the oven and let cool slightly.",
    "Serve the lamb and pear mixture hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
